Module org.monarchinitiative.phenol.io
Package org.monarchinitiative.phenol.io

Class MinimalOntologyLoader

java.lang.Object
org.monarchinitiative.phenol.io.MinimalOntologyLoader
public class MinimalOntologyLoader extends Object
Entry class for loading a MinimalOntology implemented using vanilla Java.

The loader methods start from a File or an InputStream and can read ontologies in OWL, OBO, or JSON format.

See OntologyLoader for more details.

Author:
Daniel Danis
